name: Fill in Invitations Boys
description:
Lil vites are simple fill in the blank invitations that are designed & printed in Australia on paper manufactured from elemental chlorine free pulp, which is harvested from sustainably & responsibly managed plantations and forests. Envelopes are also made in Australia using Australian Recycled paper stocks. Packs come complete with magnets for easy fridge mount.

Sold in full packs only. 8 Invitations per pack.

name: Milk Log
description:
Milk logs are the prefect companion for mums that enjoy keeping baby's feeding records, babys that are cared for by others and for those with fussy feeders!

J'Adore Baby has created beautifully handcrafted string bound journals that any mum would be proud to carry. 

Here at J'Adore baby we understand that some baby's are bottle or express fed and have made allowances for this within our milk logs.

Varied designs available please check our Facebook page and specify which design you are after.
